Mailing lists
-------------

   There is NO mailing list used to discuss libenchant specificly as yet.  For now
please use the AbiWord-devel list. To subscribe send a mail to:

	abiword-dev-request@abisource.com
And in the body of the message write "subscribe"

An archive of the mailing lists is available in:
	http://www.abisource.com/mailinglists/abiword-dev/

